http://xunitpatterns.com

Important annotations used:

@RunWith(MockitoJUnitRunner.class)

@Test
@Mock : if you are mocking something , then u can provide the default parameter and what it should return.
@InjectMocks
@MockBean : adds the bean to the spring application context if it is not already present.


@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)
@SpringBootTest(webEnvironment=WebEnvironment.RANDOM_PORT) : for integration test
@TestPropertySource(locations= {"classpath:test-configuration.properties"})

@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)
@WebMvcTest(ItemController.class)

@ContextConfiguration
@Import

@RunWith(SpringRunner.class)
@DataJpaTest //important for testing the repository class.creates all the database related connections with this annotation.


Libraries : 

Assert
hamcrest
Assertion

